---
title: Lemony Pan-Seared Chicken with Pesto Potato Salad and Peas
description: Prepared pesto is one of our favourite shortcuts in the kitchen – it adds incredible flavour in no time at all. Tossed with sweet peas and crunchy pine nuts, it gives this potato salad serious oomph. A squeeze of lemon wakes the whole dish up.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lemony-pan-seared-chicken-8b4568.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/lemony-pan-seared-chicken-8b4568.pdf
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
